    Black Aracnia suddenly realized Darkmouse was gone. On the monitors she 
saw Quickstrike and Megatron, but the monitor with the rodent on it just 
showed the hatch, she was gone.
    "Damn it! I know there up to something.....especially that rat." She 
hissed.
    
    Adrax entered the room with the transport. It was a fine ship and would 
certianly aid them in the extermination of the Maximals. But, for the moment, 
he was ease-dropping on the conversation between Megatron and Black Aracnia 
via a deflector dish stationed on top of the lair.
    "If negotiations go well then the Predacons will be unstoppable! And 
mabey you, Autofire, could lead the Predacons. We will wait and see. Right 
now things are far to sensitive to barge in and make demands."
